that's the way to do it. And I think a shotgun

985
00:57:53.498 --> 00:57:57.288
approach with 50 cancers is not a good idea, because I'm in Ruth's camp

986
00:57:57.298 --> 00:57:59.728
overall about the concerns about harms. That's my argument.

987
00:57:59.738 --> 00:58:02.718
Yeah. Just one more thing. I agree, but also the

