00:58:11.958 --> 00:58:15.778
I don't think we are there yet in terms of having a real sensitivity

991
00:58:15.838 --> 00:58:16.878
for early stages.

992
00:58:17.418 --> 00:58:17.728
No, no, no.

993
00:58:17.738 --> 00:58:18.968
And the specificity that is required.

994
00:58:19.058 --> 00:58:22.438
Yeah, no. Absolutely. Of course, sensitivity is the most important. Well, valuable.

995
00:58:22.518 --> 00:58:24.338
But I'm getting at the uncertainty of the-

