00:59:18.478 --> 00:59:22.138
You can't ignore the fact. And if you just go, "Well, I only want

1012
00:59:22.638 --> 00:59:24.118
single site screening," well,

1013
00:59:25.278 --> 00:59:28.818
the only thing we've got in the last 30 years is lung.

1014
00:59:28.918 --> 00:59:31.058
That is not the way to make progress.

1015
00:59:32.138 --> 00:59:36.018
Single site, I agree with you that single site, I will

1016
00:59:36.138 --> 00:59:39.878
