00:59:48.218 --> 00:59:51.548
that, too. But I agree with you. The signals,

1020
00:59:51.858 --> 00:59:55.118
mutations, fragmentomics, methylation, they are common among

1021
00:59:55.138 --> 00:59:59.108
cancers. So if you say, "I want to find only pancreatic cancer," let's

1022
00:59:59.138 --> 01:00:02.998
say, you're going to find more breast cancers, for example, if it's a

