1046
01:01:25.078 --> 01:01:27.518
I think the real harms come from false

1047
01:01:27.578 --> 01:01:30.842
positivesThe ensuing workup,

1048
01:01:31.122 --> 01:01:32.702
complications of the workup,

1049
01:01:33.902 --> 01:01:37.592
and if the behavior of screened individuals

1050
01:01:37.662 --> 01:01:41.002
really is modified so that they skip effective screening, and

1051
01:01:42.422 --> 01:01:45.202
that's really what we need to focus on.

1052
01:01:46.162 --> 01:01:47.372
My second comment is,

1053
01:01:48.242 --> 01:01:51.982
I love Ruth's talk about what we can learn from UKC

