1065
01:02:30.502 --> 01:02:33.762
prostate oncologist. So let's focus on what went right.

1066
01:02:33.842 --> 01:02:37.442
And many of the cancers we're looking for are more like colorectal

1067
01:02:37.502 --> 01:02:41.162
